  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>chicken breast portion[s] </strong>to a bowl and sprinkle over your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>cumin</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>coriander</strong> and a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spiced chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1717660361052-x200.jpg",
