    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> spiced chicken</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side, or until browned</p>",
