        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>chicken tinga</strong>, <strong>grated cheese</strong> and <strong>lime mayo</strong> evenly between the <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>tortillas </strong>– these are your <strong>chicken breast tinga tacos</strong></p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
